    <mxCell id="notes" value="Notes &amp; Metadata&#10;&#10;&#8226; Frequency: monthly feed; volume ~8,000 CTRs/month; retention 10 years (US compliance).&#10;&#8226; Integration: NDM file drop (no manual intervention) &#8211; source is a legacy System of Record; automated, traceable lineage. Lineage documented in Data Catalog.&#10;&#8226; DB connections: ODBC (load/staging) and JDBC (backend reads report table). APIs exposed for dashboard only; no downstream apps.&#10;&#8226; CRC DB hosted on ICRM DB ORAAS; app on OpenShift (Citi PaaS); UI served by Apache.&#10;&#8226; OPEN ISSUE: governance directive may require a new CSI for the new app/schema (currently reusing 176042) &#8211; pending confirmation.&#10;&#8226; Acronyms: NDM=Network Data Mover; CTR=Cash Transaction Report; CRC=Citi Risk &amp; Controls; ICRM=Independent Compliance Risk Mgmt; ORAAS=Oracle RAC as a Service; SoR=System of Record." style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;shape=mxgraph.basic.document;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;dashed=1;dashPattern=12 12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
